@startuml
title ATM Control - Greet User and Check PIN

[*] --> Greeting

state Greeting
Greeting : do / Display Welcome Message

state InsertingCard
InsertingCard : do / Card Inserted

state CheckingPIN
CheckingPIN : entry / Card inserted
CheckingPIN : do / Validate PIN
CheckingPIN : exit / Valid PIN

CheckingPIN --> InvalidPIN
InvalidPIN : entry / Incorrect PIN
InvalidPIN : do / Ask for PIN again
InvalidPIN --> CheckingPIN

CheckingPIN --> SecurityHold : [Too Many Attempts] /\nCard Confiscated, Update Status
SecurityHold : exit / Display Confiscated

CheckingPIN --> ReturnCard : Cancel / Eject
ReturnCard : exit / Display Ejected

ValidPIN --> Options
Options : entry / Valid PIN
Options : do / Display Menu

state Withdrawal
Withdrawal : entry / Select Withdrawal
Withdrawal : do / Request Withdrawal, Display Wait

state CheckingInformation
CheckingInformation : entry / Select Check Information
CheckingInformation : do / Show Account Info

state MakingTransfer
MakingTransfer : entry / Select Make Transfer
MakingTransfer : do / Transfer Funds

Options --> Withdrawal
Options --> CheckingInformation
Options --> MakingTransfer

Withdrawal --> ProcessingWithdrawal
ProcessingWithdrawal --> Dispensing : Withdrawal Approved /\nDispense Cash, Update Status
ProcessingWithdrawal --> Ejecting : Rejected / Eject

CheckingInformation --> ReturnCard : Cancel / Eject
MakingTransfer --> ReturnCard : Cancel / Eject

Ejecting --> Terminating : Card Ejected / Display Ejected
@enduml
